  "title": "Events Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Company</strong></p><p><em>Be part of a fast-paced and growing organisation that values teamwork, collaboration, and an open working culture. We encourage employees to take ownership of their roles, demonstrate initiative in their daily tasks, and grow together with the organisation.</em></p><p><em>We welcome well-rounded individuals who are motivated to learn, develop new skills, and contribute positively in a dynamic environment.</em></p><p></p><p><strong>What We Provide</strong></p><ul><li>Structured 1-to-1 mentorship with experienced professionals</li><li>Hands-on training with readily available skillsets</li><li>Supportive learning environment to develop professional and interpersonal skills</li></ul><p> <strong>What We Offer</strong></p><ul><li>Clear career progression opportunities</li><li>A family-oriented and collaborative work culture</li><li>Exposure to exciting overseas opportunities, subject to role requirements</li></ul><p> <strong>What We Are Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>Highly motivated individuals with a strong learning mindset</li><li>Ability to adapt and perform in a fast-paced work environment</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Willingness to take initiative and responsibility in assigned tasks</li><li>Team players who value collaboration and continuous improvement</li></ul><p></p>",
